item.title: Cant get online
item.dc:creator: @J03RY J03RY
item.description:
@J03RY wrote:

Like i said, if you cant go on 127.0.0.1 then your server is not online.
Becouse you couild even connect to 127.0.0.1 if you dont have internet. (trust me, my internet was down last week and i kept coding my server becouse it was the only game i could connect to w/o internet)

maybe look for a new Run.bat file or something? but its not your router … the server is just not online…
Or the port inside the client or server is not correclty set… dont think about your router… you only need to set your router once you where able to get on your server.
if you cant then no1 will.
